{"tid":1627981,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實你班友識唔識打交？鶳極都企得返起身周圍走","createTime":"2019-10-05T19:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:37:02.000Z","uid":34241,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"732bc3da059e63b56cf3b9d1c6c353c8ff5698e9","tid":1627981,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:48:39.000Z","msg":"究竟係藍屍太重防定你地唔識打交？<br />\n10幾條友擸埋架生去圍毆1個人<br />\n個個都按摩咁既力，有D連點樣棒打都唔識<br />\n仲有人拎支鬼死咁長既竹舉高想揮棒扑落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟點樣圍毆先可以爆哂缸但四肢健全、行得走得、 返轉頭拎刀劈柒你都仲得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未睇過古惑仔？<br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪冇食飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪唔記得有手足比人斬到見骨 斬到要坐輪椅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鶳係象徵式架咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亂咁打就似暴徒<br />\n有方法有技巧咁打咪叫正義之師囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5104c2968188f800291ba10cea84d4d78d67eb","tid":1627981,"uid":157522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04214b6ad6173d37d931587a39036defb3a23bfa","tid":1627981,"uid":120742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:57:18.000Z","msg":"一定要打碎膝頭同手踭"},{"pid":"37e94747c187003c39f8c4f7b71a7c4558723aba","tid":1627981,"uid":53610,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T21:04:20.000Z","msg":"其實落唔到手打死人/打殘人都理解嘅，但係捉到狗係咪起碼應該綁起佢遊街/做俘虜呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解次次打完人都由得佢走，咁樣對家兵力永遠都唔會減少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbddd1632dc0c276189da3d657833b7d7bbe062","tid":1627981,"uid":212336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T21:14:57.000Z","msg":"本身呢幾幾代都唔係打交大,低已經唔靚<br />\n<br />\n仲成撚日話唔出人命,呢到又留力<br />\n<br />\n扣咗呢兩樣,對人殺傷有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bea3ce4b2816c812033b856699c55fde56eede4","tid":1627981,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:34:54.000Z","msg":"當對家以殺死示威者為目標<br />\n香港人居然以幫對方R痕做目標，仲話見紅好收手喇、畫面唔好睇、文宣好難做、國際戰線又輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港果然係左膠之都 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b1ba5ac6141c9268b459500c7999e21b3d9e31","tid":1627981,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"連我個自稱中立的阿婆都話<br />\n你班示威者除左爆玻璃仲識做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打人都唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6969dbdb9d637729ef15097a5abff176116c02c2","tid":1627981,"uid":132488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/aa/65/68/aa6568bbfe818161522b8fbcdd55c289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Faa%2F65%2F68%2Faa6568bbfe818161522b8fbcdd55c289.jpg&h=a3323b3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"810e0c14d7e2255f0a9ce76966f77eb35b78b4b8","tid":1627981,"uid":258958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"一定要拗關節！ 手尾長 又快！<br />\n班狗教ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb4c063deff5175833ec5b7f3270176f1e972d","tid":1627981,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:44:17.000Z","msg":"傘揮擊係無能用"},{"pid":"8811d9acdc551cf5211897d97c3959635e926b1c","tid":1627981,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"斷關節 又快又長手尾<br />\n冇返幾個月都斬唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4137760125c8690432ab5ac0c151619137a115e8","tid":1627981,"uid":34410,"like":0,"disl